data.description: PRICE ADJUSTMENT- Welcome to this amazing 4 bedroom, 3 bath home in the heart of the charming city of Justin. This former model home is a prized gem with multiple upgrades, boasting over 3,000 square feet.  The first floor invites you in with wall to wall hands scraped hardwood floors in the living areas, a beautiful stone fireplace, a spacious kitchen with an extended bar, plenty of cabinetry, a formal dining room,  first floor primary bedroom and gorgeous bath along with two additional ample sized bedrooms with yet another first floor bath plus an office. Upstairs you will find a private haven with a cinema or media room, loft and an additional spacious bedroom and bathroom! perfect for a mother in law suite or college student. This house is ready to be your next home with plenty of room for everybody.  All this space in a lower tax bracket with super low HOA.  VA loan assumable! Close to elementary school, and plenty options for dining! Make this your next home!
